OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773316978
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in Co
OL,4,CFermanagh
OL,6,FA 45-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder over the death of a 23-
OL,8,Fyear-old woman in Co Fermanagh.
OL,10,FEllie Flanagan was found dead in the
OL,11,FCorban Avenue area of Enniskillen, by
OL,12,Fofficers who were carrying out
OL,13,Finquiries relating to a crash on the
OL,14,FCarn Road near Tempo at about 9.15pm
OL,15,Fon Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
