PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773316978
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in Co
OL,4,CFermanagh
OL,6,FThe statement the PSNI said: "Major
OL,7,FInvestigation Team detectives,
OL,8,Finvestigating the murder of Ellie
OL,9,FFlanagan in Enniskillen, have charged
OL,10,Fa 45-year-old man with murder and
OL,11,Fpossession of an offensive weapon with
OL,12,Fintent.
OL,14,F"He is due to appear before Strabane
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday 12th
OL,16,FMarch via video link."
OL,18,FOn Monday, Detective Chief Inspector
OL,19,FGary Robinson said: "Our thoughts are
OL,20,Ffirmly with Ellie's family and loved
OL,21,Fones at this very distressing time."
OL,26,@nD@^OUvD@AOUxD@VO]{D@UOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
