PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773316978
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in Co
OL,4,CFermanagh
OL,6,FMr Robinson added: "Our team continues
OL,7,Fto work at pace to establish the
OL,8,Fcircumstances surrounding Ellie's
OL,9,Fdeath and to determine exactly what
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,F"I would reiterate our appeal to
OL,13,Fanyone who may have information that
OL,14,Fcould assist us, to contact police on
OL,15,F101, quoting reference number 1564 07/
OL,16,F03/26. Any detail, no matter how
OL,17,Fsmall, could prove crucial to our
OL,18,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@nD@TOUtD@AOU
