PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1773316978
OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in Co
OL,4,CFermanagh
OL,6,F"We urge anyone who was travelling on
OL,7,Fthe Cornagrade Road into Corban Avenue
OL,8,Fbetween 6.30pm and 10.45pm on Saturday
OL,9,Fevening and noticed anything out of
OL,10,Fthe ordinary, or suspicious, to make
OL,11,Fcontact with us.
OL,13,F"The local community will continue to
OL,14,Fsee a police presence in the Corban
OL,15,FAvenue area over the coming days, as
OL,16,Four investigation develops."
